    dc:title="because democracy is an idea that has..."
    dc:identifier="http://www.notapathetic.com/comments/500"
    dc:description="because democracy is an idea that has passed its sell-by date. Rather than entrusting our liberties to unemployable political careerists who will do anything for power we should be looking for a better post-democratic..."
